casebody.data:
Donald J. TRUMP, President of the United States, et al., petitioners,
v.
INTERNATIONAL REFUGEE ASSISTANCE PROJECT, et al. No. 16-1436. Supreme Court of the United States June 2, 2017.

The respondents are directed to file a response to the petition for writ of certiorari on or before 3 p.m., Monday, June 12, 2017.
